==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Jah'''
#shortened form of [[Jehovah]], God's personal name in the [[Bible]]. Often appearing as part of Biblical names as "-iah", or "Jeho-" as in Isaiah, Jeremiah, Jehoshua, and Jehosaphat, and Hebrew words like "[[Hallelujah]]".
